How to deploy werchan on your own site
======================================

1. Follow the werc installation instructions in README
2. Create a cronjob to run bin/prune.rc and delete old threads
3. Rename sites/guhnoo.org to match your domain
4. Edit sites/your_site/_werc/config
5. Edit sites/your_site/*.html
6. Add admin badges to sites/your_site/team/
7. Remove or replace the advertisement in sites/your_site/_werc/lib/footer.inc
8. Remove boards that you do not want under sites/your_site/
9. Create boards
   i) Copy sites/your_site/example to sites/your_site/board_name
  ii) Edit sites/your_site/board_name/_werc/config
 iii) Add board_name to bin/prune.rc
  iv) Add board_name to sites/your_site/board_name/_werc/lib/top_bar.inc
